data.description: Lovely country setting, on just over an acre! This 3/ 4-bedroom home offer lots of possibilities!  With two bedrooms and the full bath on the main level, this layout is sure to please.  Upstairs you will find LARGE loft area that would be great for an additional bedroom/office/craft area etc, plus one additional bedroom.  This home has lots of hardwood floors that are ready for your finishing touches! Home needs TLC and offers lots of potential! The one car garage is just steps from the home. This home is conveniently situated so that there is ample room for a large garden, places to ride your toys or potentially an additional outbuilding! Don't delay, this is a great price for this country setting!
